DESCRIPTION:Breaking news: the infamous Serial Friendship Killer has finall
 y been caught. After years of ghosting\, emotional negligence and catastrop
 hic social behaviour\, one gay man stands trial for the countless friendshi
 ps he may or may not have ruined along the way. Part courtroom drama\, part
  public execution\, "Confessions of a Serial Friendship Killer" is a darkly
  funny one-man show exploring intimacy\, loneliness and the emotionally unh
 inged decisions we make in the name of connection. Featuring former best fr
 iends\, queer friendships with questionable boundaries\, Pokémon card blac
 kmail and the existential horror of losing a friend to motherhood\, this co
 nfessional comedy asks one important question: When does a friendship end..
 . and who gets custody of the trauma?\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/c
 omedy-atlas/event/confessions-of-a-serial-friendship-killer/
